description: Breathtaking corner 2 bedroom plus den, 2.5 bathroom home with expansive views of the Harbor, North End, and airport. This magnificent sun-filled home features a graciously sized living room with custom built-ins, dramatic floor-to-ceiling windows, an open kitchen that is appointed exquisitely with custom cabinets and top of the line appliances by Wolf, Miele and SubZero. The Primary suite has a corner exposure and a stunning spa-like bathroom with double vanity, marble soaking tub, and glass shower. The private second bedroom has an en-suite bathroom, and down a hallway leads to a spacious bonus room ideal for a home office or guest room. Tandem parking space for 2 cars in the garage directly below the building and an additional storage unit are included in this offering. Twenty Two Liberty features a collection of amenities including 24 hour concierge, doorman, fitness center, board room and entertaining space with terrace. Just steps from Boston's best restaurants and shopping.
